6月30日，“南方之星号”（{{lang|en|Star of the South}}）船只在[[美国东岸|美国东岸]]近海遭遇强风<ref name="partagas-1" />。据大西洋飓风数据库记载，本季第一个热带气旋于[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]6月30日凌晨0点在[[北卡罗莱纳州|北卡罗莱纳州]][[哈特拉斯角|哈特拉斯角]]（{{lang|en|Cape Hatteras}}）东南方向约160公里海域成型<ref name="HURDAT">{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | author2 = Hurricane Research Division | title = Atlantic hurricane best track (HURDAT version 2) | accessdate = 2016-11-01 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-070616.txt | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2016-07-06 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-10-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161004150702/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-070616.txt | format = [[文本文件|TXT]] }}</ref>。风暴朝正东略偏北面行进，风速为每小时95公里<ref name="HURDAT" />。7月1日，“弗吉尼亚号”（{{lang|en|Virginia}}）[[三桅帆船|三桅帆船]]在[[百慕大|百慕大]]西北偏北425公里洋面发现风暴，此后气旋便失去踪影<ref name="partagas-1" /><ref name="HURDAT" />。
